    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-maintained throughout its life. The paint still holds a great shine, though there are some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few faint surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of major wear, with all electronics and climate controls functioning as they should. Mechanically, the car starts reliably and drives smoothly, showing that it has been serviced regularly. It\u2019s a dependable, attractive choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that is ready for the road.",
      "price": 36500.0,
